otics Deal：&lt;/strong&gt;瑞士工业巨头ABB Ltd.正在探索&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qYUnd-Nix5fmrz5CPbKaGGG8UHzkPzbhQBfs9dmYZZ5sqtgyjHrMCaKFfo-u0IVHknRFdCdYSjbC9XKjXFONAdY7ATOB6kjJmlmJ5LZzsHvOHbZoTXszkyCot4fch0QoymJ7YVXsbZrUmCsN76Ws7HbK_81Ag-bDKrQk2qjhbB-KaC8aPtEtNxC9IOHekWUgQhIkDe3CPdtgu8tgsKWTZ-ZQhcikDVOXafCSHvB4PxoH1moLabV-JUapZxwxAUXZ1Ba_yIpOHj9lb8juw74qbkKr8A/dNo3h9QA-0O8eD6hm3YUGt59ED5C_nqP/8" target="_blank" title="链接到故事"&gt;机器人部门的潜在出售，该单位的&lt;/a&gt;价值可能超过35亿美元，以替代销售业务。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px 8px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2"&gt;相关故事&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: #CCC; border-bottom-style: solid; padding: 16px 8px 9px 0px;" valign="top" width="129"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/E4ZiUVmrpyNbuT11A3TA1WevV5lj1x3c8qh6G-0SntkTc_apZvlbREMW_H3EGxcWJi61kaDpF70C0WQHCLrjp-asTEt9_h29CFGMimaZzQ90HOIZ1mEkaJtW_hcydNwVIa_Mf-t4MdUiAJhu4SUA1H0LZg3wOZVsdiltaCWxTwLX4GwQhTkdkwcIi21VyLef00XLhbmfuCdzADif5WIGqfHZfLZ2oUxBbT2efplkJHi1g2vSQGJjY3yqnmoxWM_IxJcuZRTF5AfmK6IsCxB9SnAjng/5D0115yKTKfsK4EWJgE1tWoW20GjI-TZ/8" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="129"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ialRhUBd.N4w/v0/129x86.jpg" width="129"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ialRhUBd.N4w/v0/129x86.jpg" style="width: auto; height: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt